Msunduzi Municipality in KwaZulu-Natal announced a new call centre number on Wednesday that is applicable with immediate effect. The new number is 087 655 5778. It said the number and the system is aimed at improving communication between customers and the municipality. It added that while migrating to the new number, the old numbers are still applicable until further notice but residents are encouraged to use the new call centre number. Emergency call centre (ECC) numbers 033 392 3725 033 392 2945 033 392 2504 Electricity fault office 033 348 2179 Water and sanitation 033 392 2133 033 392 2759